                        <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 814.51/243.</note>
                        <head ana="#head_untitled-inferred-from-preceding-sibling-head">[Untitled]</head>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>, <lb/>
                                    <hi rend="italic">Guatemala</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1913-05-06">
                                    <hi rend="italic">May 6, 1913</hi></date>.</dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>The British Legation has informed me that a British cruiser has arrived
                            at Belize.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Wilson</hi>.</signed>
                        </closer>
